ks, savings banks, and U.S. branches of foreign banks, and the OTS surveys all savings associations. Prior to 1997, the FDIC and the OTS published bank and thrift deposit data separately in printed Data Books. Beginning with the 1997 Data Book, information covering all banks and savings associations has been combined into a single publication. The results for individual institution offices, organized by state, are published in six regional Data Books. Aggregate data for the U.S., states, counties and other areas are published in the national Data Book.  aDescription based on online resource; title from collection home page (FRASER, viewed March 10, 2026). 0aBank depositszUnited StatesvStatistics. 0aBank depositszUnited StatesxStates. 0aBank accountszUnited StatesvStatistics. 0aBank accountszUnited StatesxStates. 7aPeriodicals.2lcgft0http://id.loc.gov/authorities/genreForms/gf2014026139 7aStatistics.2lcgft0http://id.loc.gov/authorities/genreForms/gf20140261811 aUnited States.bOffice of Thrift Supervision,eauthor.0http://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/no8901365408iTitle in collection:aFederal Deposit Insurance Corporation.tAccounts and deposits of insured commercial banks, November 18, 1964.w(OCoLC)21498908iTitle in collection:tSummary of accounts and deposits in all commercial banks ...w(OCoLC)238327608iTitle in collection:tSummary of accounts and deposits in all mutual savings banksw(OCoLC)313155208iTitle in collection:aFederal Deposit Insurance Corporation.tSummary of deposits in all commercial and mutual savings banksw(OCoLC)179146808iTitle in collection:tSummary of accounts and deposits in all commercial and mutual savings banks. National summaryw(OCoLC)283017408iTitle in collection:tBanks & branches data bookw(OCoLC)829198208iTitle in collection:tData book, operating banks and branchesw(OCoLC)1105681640zAvailable at FRASERuhttps://purl.fdlp.gov/GPO/gpo253758704 zAddress at time of PURL creationuht